---
// ImageShowcase.astro — Enhanced (Format A + Visual Comparison)
---

<section id="image-showcase" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">

    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 class="section-heading">Failure Case: Stale Perception Under Vibration</h2>

    <!-- Short explanation (Format A style) -->
    <p class="section-intro">
      Under real-world vibration, redundant and distorted sensor streams delay critical observations. 
      As a result, perception operates on stale inputs—leading to missed detections and unsafe decisions.
    </p>

    <div class="image-groups">
      <div class="image-group">

        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="group-description">
          The left shows failure under vibration-induced stale perception, while the right highlights improved sensing with adaptive filtering.
        </p>

        <!-- Comparison -->
        <div class="image-pair">

          <!-- BEFORE -->
          <div class="image-card">
            <span class="tag tag-bad">Stale Perception</span>

            <iframe 
              src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1R2sQOs8LKBlH2kDEpd74cFOKFQpBsW0X/preview"
              allow="autoplay"
              title="Failure video">
            </iframe>
          </div>

          <!-- AFTER -->
          <div class="image-card">
            <span class="tag tag-good">Adaptive Sensing</span>

            <img 
              src="https://drive.google.com/thumbnail?id=1RfFGE0oFWyu_Y5CMWwD_ZAvSUXCY-Ycw&sz=w1000"
              alt="Improved sensing"
            />
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>

/* ===== INTRO ===== */
.section-intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  max-width: 900px;
  text-align: justify;
}

/* ===== DESCRIPTION ===== */
.group-description {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #666;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

/* ===== PAIR ===== */
.image-pair {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.4rem;
}

/* ===== CARD ===== */
.image-card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 14px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #111;

  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;

  border: 1px solid #e4e8ef;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.image-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

/* ===== MEDIA ===== */
.image-card iframe,
.image-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border: none;
  transition: transform 0.4s ease;
}

.image-card:hover img,
.image-card:hover iframe {
  transform: scale(1.04);
}

/* ===== TAGS ===== */
.tag {
  position: absolute;
  top: 12px;
  left: 12px;
  padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  border-radius: 20px;
  color: white;
  z-index: 2;
}

.tag-bad {
  background: rgba(200, 60, 60, 0.9);
}

.tag-good {
  background: rgba(40, 140, 90, 0.9);
}

/* ===== HEADING ===== */
.section-heading {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}

.section-heading::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -6px;
  left: 0;
  width: 55px;
  height: 3px;
  background: #c05e3c;
}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .image-pair {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: left;
  }
}

</style>